#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, "
"floppy and &CD; drives, USB sticks &etc;) along with information on their "
"capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and "
"unmount drives and view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; उपलब्धसञ्चिकायन्त्राणि (हार्डड्राइवविभाजनं, फ्लॉपी तथा &CD;ड्राइव्, USB "
"स्टिक & इत्यादयः) तेषां क्षमता, मुक्तस्थानं, प्रकारः, माउण्ट् बिन्दुः च इति सूचनाभिः सह "
"प्रदर्शयति इदं भवन्तं ड्राइव्-माउण्ट्-अनमाउण्ट्-करणं च सञ्चिका-प्रबन्धके द्रष्टुं च शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; is similar to the &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, but "
"takes up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
"window available at all times."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, परन्तु स्क्रीनस्थानं न्यूनं "
"गृह्णाति । यदि भवान् &kdiskfree; सर्वदा उपलब्धं विण्डो।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "&kdiskfree इत्यस्य उपयोगेन;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "आरभ्य &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
"select <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and &kde; "
"command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at the "
"command prompt."
msgstr ""
"प्रकारः<userinput><command> kdf</command></userinput> आदेशप्रोम्प्ट् इत्यत्र अथवा "
"चयनं कुर्वन्तु<guimenuitem> KDiskFree इति</guimenuitem> इति<guisubmenu> व्यवस्था</"
"guisubmenu> अनुप्रयोगप्रक्षेपके समूहः । मानकं &amp;Qt; तथा &amp;kde; आदेशविकल्पाः "
"उपलभ्यन्ते, प्रविष्ट्वा च सूचीकृतुं शक्यन्ते<userinput><command> kdf</command><option "
"value=--help> --साहाय्यम्‌</option></userinput> आदेशप्रोम्प्ट् इत्यत्र ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application as an applet in the systemtray, use "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in application launcher."
msgstr ""
"एप्लिकेशनं सिस्टम्ट्रे एप्लेट् रूपेण चालयितुं, एप्लिकेशन लॉन्चर् मध्ये "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The features of &kdiskfree; are also available in the &systemsettings; "
"module <guilabel>Storage Devices</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree इत्यस्य विशेषताः; &systemsettings; module <guilabel>भण्डारणयन्त्राणि</"
"guilabel> ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main window"
msgstr "मुख्यविण्डो इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."
msgstr "मुख्यं &kdiskfree; विण्डो उपलब्धानि सञ्चिकायन्त्राणि प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are included:"
msgstr "सामान्यतया निम्नलिखितसूचनाः समाविष्टाः भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<स्क्रीनसूचना>&kdiskfree; स्क्रीन</screeninfo> इति"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<वाक्यांश>&kdiskfree; पटल</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "भण्डारणस्य प्रकारं चित्रयति इति चिह्नम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "यन्त्रनाम"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "filesystem type"
msgstr "सञ्चिकातन्त्रप्रकारः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "कुल आकार"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "माउण्ट बिन्दु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "मुक्त डिस्क स्थानं"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "संख्यारूपेण आलेखरूपेण च प्रयुक्तस्य स्थानस्य प्रतिशतम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> कस्यचित् स्तम्भविशेषस्य शीर्षकं नुत्वा तस्य चरस्य अनुसारं "
"उपकरणानि क्रमेण भवन्ति । द्वितीयं <mousebutton>वाम</mousebutton> क्लिक् विपरीतक्रमेण "
"क्रमयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on a row pops up a menu. If that device is not "
"currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> option is "
"available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Open in "
"File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a graphical view of the "
"files on that device."
msgstr ""
"&RMB इत्यनेन सह क्लिक् कृत्वा; पङ्क्तौ मेनू दृश्यते । यदि तत् यन्त्रं सम्प्रति माउण्ट् न भवति "
"तर्हि <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> विकल्पः उपलभ्यते । यदि यन्त्रं माउण्ट् "
"कृतम् अस्ति तर्हि <guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem> इति चित्वा तत् अनमाउण्ट् "
"कर्तुं शक्यते । <guimenuitem>सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धके उद्घाटय</guimenuitem> इति चित्वा तस्मिन् "
"यन्त्रे सञ्चिकानां चित्रात्मकदृश्येन सह नूतनं विण्डो उद्घाट्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting for the file manager used by &kdiskfree; is independent from the "
"choice in the &systemsettings; module <guilabel>Default Applications</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; &systemsettings; module <guilabel>पूर्वनिर्धारित अनुप्रयोगाः</"
"guilabel> ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar and Configuration"
msgstr "मेनू बार तथा विन्यास"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "सञ्चिकामेनू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>अद्यतनं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Immediately updates the display to reflect the current status"
msgstr "वर्तमानस्थितिं प्रतिबिम्बयितुं तत्क्षणमेव प्रदर्शनं अद्यतनं करोति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निर्गम</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Closes</action> &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "<action>निमीलति</action> &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &kdiskfree; किञ्चित् सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् संवादः"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु &kdiskfree; स्क्रीन</screeninfo> इति"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु &kdiskfree; पटल</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has two tabbed windows, <guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Mount Commands</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् संवादे <guilabel>सामान्यसेटिंग्स्</guilabel> तथा <guilabel>माउण्ट् आदेशाः</"
"guilabel> इति ट्याब्ड् विण्डोद्वयम् अस्ति"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "सामान्य सेटिंग्स्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the word <guilabel>visible</guilabel> or <guilabel>hidden</"
"guilabel> to turn display of an data field on or off."
msgstr ""
"दत्तांशक्षेत्रस्य प्रदर्शनं चालू अथवा निष्क्रियं कर्तुं <guilabel>visible</guilabel> अथवा "
"<guilabel>hidden</guilabel> इति शब्दं नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the update frequency by editing the value. The value in the box is "
"the interval (in seconds) between updates of the &kdiskfree; display to "
"reflect the current status."
msgstr ""
"मूल्यं सम्पादयित्वा अद्यतन-आवृत्तिं परिवर्तयन्तु । पेटीयां मूल्यं &kdiskfree; वर्तमानस्थितिं "
"प्रतिबिम्बयितुं प्रदर्शनम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> setting controls the command executed "
"when the <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup menu item is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकः</guilabel> सेटिङ्ग् <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</"
"guimenuitem> पॉपअप मेनू-वस्तु चयनं भवति तदा निष्पादितं आदेशं नियन्त्रयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two check boxes. One controls if a file manager window will "
"be automatically opened when a device is mounted. The other causes an alert "
"window to pop up if a disk gets critically full."
msgstr ""
"तत्र द्वौ चेकबॉक्सौ अपि स्तः । एकः नियन्त्रयति यत् यदि यन्त्रस्य आरोहणं भवति तदा "
"सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकविण्डो स्वयमेव उद्घाट्यते वा । अन्यः कारणं भवति यत् यदि डिस्कः गम्भीररूपेण "
"पूर्णः भवति तर्हि अलर्ट् विण्डो पोप् अप भवति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Commands"
msgstr "माउण्ट् आदेशाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the user to specify the mount and unmount commands for a given "
"device, as well as the icon used to represent it. More information on these "
"commands can be found on the man page for <application>mount</application> "
"(type <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput> "
"at the command prompt)."
msgstr ""
"उपयोक्तारं दत्तस्य यन्त्रस्य कृते माउण्ट्-अनमाउण्ट्-आदेशान्, तस्य प्रतिनिधित्वार्थं प्रयुक्तं चिह्नं च "
"निर्दिष्टुं शक्नोति । एतेषां आदेशानां विषये अधिका सूचना for man page इत्यत्र "
"प्राप्यते<application> माउण्ट्</application> (प्रकारः<userinput><command> नरः</"
"command><option value=mount> माउण्ट्</option></userinput> आदेशप्रोम्प्ट् इत्यत्र) ।"

